headline: CCL- After Another Great Quarter, Give this Cruise Line Stock a Look
summary: Carnival Corp. (CCL) recently posted another record quarter. People are still cruising – and this Zacks Rank #1 (Strong Buy) is expected to grow earnings by 47.9% this year, highlights Tracey Ryniec, senior stock strategist at Zacks Investment Research.
